msgid "Enable AI grammar checker (Writer)"
msgstr "Aktifkan pemeriksa tata bahasa AI (Writer)"

msgid ""
"When on, WriterAgent registers its AI grammar proofreader with Linguistic; "
"checked text uses your API (Tools → Options → AI). Underlines appear shortly "
"after you pause typing. Off by default."
msgstr ""
"Saat diaktifkan, WriterAgent mendaftarkan pemeriksa tata bahasa AI-nya "
"dengan Linguistic; teks yang diperiksa menggunakan API Anda (Tools → Options "
"→ AI). Garis bawah muncul segera setelah Anda berhenti mengetik. Dimatikan "
"secara default."

msgid "Grammar check wait timeout (ms)"
msgstr "Batas waktu tunggu pemeriksaan tata bahasa (ms)"

msgid ""
"Reserved for possible future use. The proofreader returns immediately on "
"cache miss (async); results appear on a later Writer pass once the sentence "
"cache is filled."
msgstr ""
"Dipesan untuk kemungkinan penggunaan di masa depan. Proofreader "
"mengembalikan hasil segera saat cache miss (async); hasil muncul pada Writer "
"pass berikutnya setelah cache kalimat terisi."

msgid "Grammar check model (optional)"
msgstr "Model pemeriksaan tata bahasa (opsional)"

msgid "Leave empty to use the same text model as chat."
msgstr "Biarkan kosong untuk menggunakan model teks yang sama seperti obrolan."

msgid "Pause grammar while chat/agent runs"
msgstr "Jeda pemeriksaan tata bahasa saat chat/agent berjalan"

msgid ""
"When on, AI grammar skips background requests while sidebar chat or agent "
"runs, to avoid concurrent API calls."
msgstr ""
"Ketika diaktifkan, pemeriksaan tata bahasa AI melewatkan permintaan latar "
"belakang saat chat sidebar atau agent berjalan, untuk menghindari panggilan "
"API secara bersamaan."

